{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Lettuce Village!</strong> You're exploring the tiny forest town's communal garage sale as Juniper, a young resident who's shy yet eager to cure her summer loneliness and maybe pick up a few trinkets along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104990/extras/junipersmall@0.2x.png?t=1732046393\" />It wouldn't be a garage sale without lots of treasures! Throughout the game, you'll be able to shop at various garage sales, yard sales, and stores to find storied antiques, homemade crafts, and sentimental trinkets that provide glimpses into their former owners' lives. (And, if you explore every nook and cranny in Lettuce Village, you'll find just enough coins to purchase every item in the sale. You're welcome.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104990/extras/antsmall@0.2x.png?t=1732046393\" />Lettuce Village is in the middle of nowhere, so your neighbors are... a bit interesting. As you explore the town, you'll have the opportunity to complete small quests to help your neighbors, rewarding you with bits of the town's history, some coins or unique items, and occasionally a lifelong friendship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104990/extras/nadiasmall3@0.2x.png?t=1732046393\" />Despite its small size, Lettuce Village has quite the interesting history. Take your time talking to your neighbors, exploring every area, and completing as many quests as you can \u2014 you just might be able to uncover some of the town's well-kept secrets...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Over 30 unique villagers to get to know through 10+ side quests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Over 75 rooms to explore, including houses, forested areas, secret passageways, and some pretty quirky surprises</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Over 50 items to collect, each with its own backstory that reveals information about the town's residents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Tens of thousands of lines of flavor text</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A heartfelt narrative about the importance of community</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> No timers, no scores, no stress!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Goodnight!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/a5e0e050c7916ea272acc5030b9c7c9fc595ef6d.jpg"},{"name":"Socialite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/a91e20924a06ad6b85ae54850d206055dc22411e.jpg"},{"name":"Casual Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/1c7935281b141bf233c5f8a287cfb15c0e561382.jpg"},{"name":"Champion Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/e788b678e06ed5122b857062144f52f91fefa506.jpg"},{"name":"Worm Whisperer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/b728b1a44f990278495429aec92d9f4255e1c98f.jpg"},{"name":"Smileberry Supporter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/543049a2bcad8daa195f41f54b86aeff486c7517.jpg"},{"name":"Long Day...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/a7379da5cc0e3f415e46323ee7fa9bb6bed1fa98.jpg"},{"name":"Just a \"J\" Will Do","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2104990/9d93e5f80ada39a70743473242cb6902f4dbbe3d.jpg"},{"name":"Roots","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstati